 Published 16 mins ago on January 12, 2021  Dolapo Grey has a shared her recipe for easy moist chocolate muffins and you should definitely try it. All-purpose flour – 2 cups
Sugar – 1 & 1/4 cup
Cocoa powder – 2/3 cup
Salt – 1/2 teaspoon
Baking powder – 2 teaspoons
Baking soda – 1/2 teaspoon
Chocolate chips – 1 cup
Eggs – 2
Buttermilk or Sour milk – 1 & 1/4 cup
Vegetable oil – 1/4 cup
Butter – 1/4 cup, melted and cooled
Vanilla – 2 teaspoon Learn the process below:   The best Nigerian and African video content from around the web specially curated for YOU! 